column5: My friend in the first picture never caught a walleye before so, the first one he ever catches is a 30" monster. Crazy eh? ? Awesome day on the lake yesterday
I see you added a kicker . Nice.

I recently ruined a friend of mine he caught a 7 lb Bass the first day out using a baitcaster for the first time. He so far has spent $400.00 or better buying a new rod and reel. He now has the bug. lol Art
Great way to introduce your friend into walleye fishing.
